msgid "For simple holiday pay recovery, you need to enter:"
msgstr "आसान हॉलिडे पे रिकवरी के लिए, आपको दर्ज करना होगा:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1757
